After 1 of your foundations is flipped by a rival effect, unflip 1 foundation.
Build 1 foundation from your hand.
After this card is unflipped, gain 1 health.
After you flip 1 or more foundations, gain 2 health.
After your rival fails a check, your next check gets +1.
After you fail a check to play a non-attack card, your Combat Phase does not end.
After you make a check, re-check by rolling a 6-sided die and using the result.
